sequenceDiagram
    actor Vendeur
    participant API Gateway
    participant Auth Middleware
    participant Tenant Middleware
    participant Eloquent ORM
    participant Database

    Vendeur->>API Gateway: GET /api/products (Authorization: Bearer Token)
    API Gateway->>Auth Middleware: Vérification du Token JWT (Sanctum)
    alt Token Invalide
        Auth Middleware-->>Vendeur: 401 Unauthorized
    else Token Valide
        Auth Middleware->>Tenant Middleware: Identifier le Tenant (store_id)
        Tenant Middleware->>Eloquent ORM: Appliquer `TenantScope` (where store_id = X)
        Eloquent ORM->>Database: SELECT * FROM products WHERE store_id = X
        Database-->>Eloquent ORM: Résultats filtrés
        Eloquent ORM-->>API Gateway: Collection JSON
        API Gateway-->>Vendeur: 200 OK (Produits isolés)
    end
